.SH NAME
ralphglasses-theme-export - Export a theme as a config snippet for another tool


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBralphglasses theme-export [format] [theme-name] [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Export a ralphglasses theme in a format suitable for other tools.

.PP
Supported formats: ghostty, starship, k9s

.PP
Examples:
  ralphglasses theme-export ghostty dracula
  ralphglasses theme-export starship nord
  ralphglasses theme-export k9s gruvbox


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for theme-export


